ealth-resource-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/megan-thee-stallion-mental-health-resource-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/megan-thee-stallion-mental-health-resource-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/megan-thee-stallion-mental-health-resource-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/megan-thee-stallion-mental-health-resource-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/megan-thee-stallion">Megan Thee Stallion</a>推出了一个新的心理健康资源网站，名为“Seize The Awkward”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/megan-thee-stallion-cover-interview-2020-girls-in-the-hood-2700621">Megan Thee Stallion：“我现在正在为我的王朝而努力”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位说唱明星本周早些时候<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/megan-thee-stallion-teases-release-of-something-that-can-help-all-of-us-3504415">在社交媒体上宣布了这项新举措</a>，并表示她即将放弃“一些可以帮助我们所有人的东西”。</p><p>昨天（9月26日）， <a href="http://SeizeTheAwkward.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《抓住尴尬》</a>官方网站上线。 “我总是被告知我必须坚强。脸皮厚。上唇僵硬。像钉子一样坚韧，”她在<a href="https://www.instagram.com/reel/CxqI6LJLA1L/?igshid=MzRlODBiNWFlZA==" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Instagram</a>上分享的一段视频中说道。</p><p> “但要为每个人提供一切——这会让你感到疲惫。他们说，“黑色不会破裂”。但它可以。我可以。我们都可以。”</p><p>她继续说道：“大家，身体不好也没关系。如果您看到朋友正在经历这种情况，请联系他们。无论你是谁，脆弱才是我们完整的原因。”</p><p>这位“Savage”歌手随后引导歌迷访问新网站以及<a href="https://www.badbitcheshavebaddaystoo.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">BadBitchesHaveBadDaysToo.com</a>以获得更多资源。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Megan Thee Stallion 谈开放 |抓住尴尬|广告委员会" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/-N7WG7dBVGw?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> 《Seize The Awkward》包含一系列视频，梅根·塞·斯塔林 (Megan Thee Stallion) 在视频中谈论了各种话题，例如关心朋友和脆弱。</p><p>还有<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noah-cyrus">诺亚·赛勒斯 (Noah Cyrus)</a> 、艾娃·马克斯 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ava-max">Ava Max</a> )、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tyler-posey">泰勒·波西 (Tyler Posey)</a>等其他明星以及美国橄榄球运动员凯莱布·威廉姆斯 (Caleb Williams) 和摔跤手 Big E 等运动员的视频。</p><p>该网站还包括一系列心理健康链接和资源，这些链接和资源是她 2022 年歌曲《焦虑》中的歌词《Bad Bitches Have Bad Days Too》的延续。</p><p> “ <em>They keep sayin&#39; I should get help / But I don&#39;t even know what I need</em> ,” she raps on the track, the visualiser for which is included on the website. </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Megan Thee Stallion - Anxiety [Official Visualizer]" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/7D85hpcSbE8?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Last month, <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tony-lanez">Tory Lanez</a> was <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tory-lanez-sentenced-to-10-years-in-prison-for-megan-thee-stallion-shooting-3480329">sentenced to 10 years in prison for shooting Megan Thee Stallion</a> . Lanez was <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tory-lanez-found-guilty-of-shooting-megan-thee-stallion-3371194">found guilty in December last year</a> of three felonies related to <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/megan-thee-stallion-reveals-she-was-shot-tory-lanez-2708559">the shooting</a> .</p><p> Megan Thee Stallion has previously spoken about the impact the attack had on her, sharing at the time that she was “hurt and traumatized”.</p><p> While she was not present at the sentencing, she submitted a court statement that read per an <a href="https://apnews.com/article/tory-lanez-sentence-megan-thee-stallion-shooting-5eeaafd1a913ebf46094bcb0358364ad" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Associated Press</em></a> report: “Since I was viciously shot by the defendant, I have not experienced a single day of peace. Slowly but surely, I&#39;m healing and coming back, but I will never be the same.”</p><p> Lanez claimed he was in <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tory-lanez-says-hes-in-great-spirits-during-first-month-in-prison-3504600">“great spirits” during the first month in prison</a> .</p><p> This month she teamed up with have teamed up with <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cardi-b">Cardi B</a> on <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-cardi-b-and-megan-thee-stallions-new-single-bongos-3494999">new single &#39;Bongos&#39;</a> .</p><p> In a recent interview with <a href="https://www.complex.com/music/a/j-mckinney/megan-thee-stallion-flamin-hot-interview" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Complex</em></a> , Megan Thee Stallion said that she was “making music that I really, really love. I&#39;m making music that I&#39;m not about to have to fight with anybody about”.</p><h2><strong>有关心理健康的帮助和建议：</strong></h2><ul><li aria-level="1"> <a href="https://www.thecalmzone.net/"><b>CALM – The Campaign Against Living Miserably</b></a></li><li aria-level="1"> <a href="https://www.helpmusicians.org.uk/"><b>Help Musicians UK – Around the clock mental health support and advice for musicians</b></a> <b>(CALL MUSIC MINDS MATTER ON: 0808 802 8008)</b></li><li aria-level="1"> <a href="http://www.musicsupport.org/"><b>Music Support Org – Help and support for musicians struggling with alcoholism, addiction, or mental health issues</b></a> <b>(CALL: 0800 030 6789)</b></li><li aria-level="1"> <a href="http://www.youngminds.org.uk/?gclid=CIuC-9ye69ICFQYo0wodX48KPA"><b>YOUNG MINDS – The voice for young people&#39;s health and wellbeing</b></a></li><li aria-level="1"> <a href="https://www.time-to-change.org.uk/"><b>Time To Change – Let&#39;s end mental health discrimination</b></a></li><li aria-level="1"><a href="http://www.samaritans.org/how-we-can-help-you/contact-us?gclid=CKyDztKf69ICFSIo0wodYjYL5A"><b>The Samaritans – Confidential support 24 hours a day</b></a></li></ul><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.